The government's decision:

In the interest of the patient in the ear, nose and throat surgery department at Vilasrao Deshmukh Government Medical College, Latur, an institution under the Department, the Government is granting administrative approval under this decision for the purchase of the equipment and equipment mentioned in the table below, subject to the following conditions, out of the total amount of Rs. 16,45,00, 000 / - (Rupees Sixteen Crores, Forty Five Lakh Only) (including all taxes) out of the proposed provision available under the State Plan.
Conditions: -
1) This administrative approval 2024-25 is being made in this financial year from the funds sanctioned and available under the State Plan to the institution concerned.
2) The Government issued a "Manual of Procedure for Office Procurement to be carried out by the Government Department" in this regard by the Department of Industries, Power and Labour.
